The simple New Zealand currency exchange site serving those trading between bitcoins and NZD

##NZD Deposits and Withdrawals

* Deposit
> Make a direct deposit into the bitNZ bank account with the particulars specifying your account details.

* Withdrawal
> To withdraw currency simply specify your New Zealand bank account number.

##Bitcoin Deposits and Withdrawals

* Deposit
> Deposit bitcoins to the bitcoin address created for your account.

* Withdrawal
> To withdraw Bitcoins simply specify a valid Bitcoin address to send to.

##Fees

* Trade Commission: 0.5%
* BTC Deposit: none
* BTC Withdrawal: 0.0005 BTC (See [[Transaction_fees]] for more information)
* NZD Deposit: none (deposits from New Zealand banks only)
* NZD Withdrawal: none (withdrawals to New Zealand banks only)

